      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "The fifth share/export surface — two new API endpoints serve per-round belief data (bullish/neutral/bearish %, agent counts, posts, engagements) as RFC 4180 CSV or newline-delimited JSON. Designed for pandas.read_csv() one-liner consumption. 17 unit tests, zero new dependencies."
      }
